8. Philosophical Premise

CLEOS is built on the principle:

“Emotions are data.”

Not gods.
Not mysteries.
Not enemies.
Not flaws.

Just signals.

When signals are made visible, they can be interpreted.
When interpreted, they can be regulated.
When regulated, the human becomes sovereign again.

CLEOS is emotional sovereignty restored through signal intelligence.

